{"an7.94:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 7.94 ","an7.94:0.2":"9. Samanavagga ","an7.94:0.3":"Saddhammasutta ","an7.94:1.1":"“Sattime, bhikkhave, saddhamma. ","an7.94:1.2":"Katame satta? ","an7.94:1.3":"Saddho hoti, hirima hoti, ottappi hoti, bahussuto hoti, araddhaviriyo hoti, satima hoti, pannava hoti. ","an7.94:1.4":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta saddhamma”ti. ","an7.94:1.5":"Dasamam. ","an7.94:1.6":"Samanavaggo navamo. ","an7.94:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","an7.94:2.1":"Bhikkhum samano brahmano, ","an7.94:2.2":"sottiyo ceva nhatako; ","an7.94:2.3":"Vedagu ariyo araha, ","an7.94:2.4":"asaddhamma ca saddhammati. "}